title: Vince Staples x Bad Rabbits -- "Made" - In The Studio
description:
Stream and download "Made" 

"Made" is the first single off of the second Converse CONS compilation, CONS EP Vol. 2, coming Summer/Fall of 2014. The song was recorded at Sunset Sound Recording Studio in Los Angeles, CA and Chicago Recording Company in Chicago Illinois. 

Produced by: Bad Rabbits 
Music by: Bad Rabbits & Vince Staples
Lyrics by: Bad Rabbits & Vince Staples
Vocals by: Bad Rabbits & Vince Staples
Talkbox Vocals by: Sergio Selim
